Apologies regarding the lull in activity. I wish I had a better work ethic than to introduce myself each time saying sorry, but anyway, I have two starts for a story I wanted to share. https://archiveofourown.org/works/33972649/chapters/84489943

This story was recommended to be made by a friend who drew the lovely picture in the beginning for a quick prompt I did. To summarize, it's a human janitor who's overly defensive interacts with a female, punk opossum who is overly aggressive due to bad experiences she's had, both romantic and non-romantic, due to her large breasts. I don't want to put her across as completely justified in being a cunt, but I do want there to be some basis for her behavior. I'm hoping to write them both earnestly and make the story more interesting than "haha big booba go boi-yoi-yoing", though that is making it difficult to justify the two continuing to hang out together with him not hesitating to call her out on her bullshit.

https://archiveofourown.org/works/33972955/chapters/84490642

The other is the apocalypse story I mentioned previously. Human woman wakes up 3 feet shorter with more hair and wolf features. Mostly everyone's dead, leaving her utterly alone, and there's other things prowling around in the sudden winter hellhole. She finds a blind human and tries to protect him. I tried to write the beginning right in the middle of her getting used to it; I wasn't satisfied with starting it right where she woke up mutated and then go through the whole process of her becoming accustomed to a post-apocalypse lifestyle, and then explain her basic story a little later near the end of the chapter. I hope that the method comes across well.

Please do let me know if anything seems wrong or poorly written. All feedback is appreciated.
